Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.72,0:00:05.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总是在思考
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.39,0:00:09.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在渡过的每一天中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.56,0:00:11.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直在思考
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.27,0:00:14.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传递不到的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.19,0:00:16.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能传递的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.86,0:00:19.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论何时，无论到何时
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.53,0:00:22.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你都毫不在意
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.20,0:00:27.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们过着不相干的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.79,0:00:30.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽管这样，还是在期待
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.63,0:00:34.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,期待？希望？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.22,0:00:39.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的话，有一个愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.89,0:00:44.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你注意到了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.47,0:00:45.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于我的事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.64,0:00:50.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我．一直．．在等待
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.40,0:00:53.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.00,0:02:59.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.58,0:03:14.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么早把我叫出来，困死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.84,0:03:21.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.68,0:03:27.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记得戴保险套哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.39,0:03:35.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想怎么样呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.77,0:04:18.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.44,0:04:21.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还想要的话，就请再付钱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.94,0:04:23.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还真贪财啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.37,0:04:39.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是特殊服务哟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.89,0:04:57.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要 KISS 吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.48,0:04:59.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋，想要做什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.28,0:05:13.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恶心的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.22,0:05:31.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就知道你会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.72,0:05:34.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！久美，你早
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.10,0:05:37.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不应该说“啊，久美”吧，穗澄
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.31,0:05:39.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么关系？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.39,0:05:43.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又不会少了什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.86,0:05:51.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了，你和朝仓君怎么样了\N已经做了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.99,0:05:56.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！什么事也没有啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.33,0:05:59.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是我喜欢的类型，我能不能出手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.96,0:06:03.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穗澄喜欢的话，我无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.30,0:06:09.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朝仓君虽然不错，可是我也想要久美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.26,0:06:12.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.14,0:06:16.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久美，你讨厌我了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.85,0:06:18.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个．．．
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.11,0:06:27.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了，回去上课了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.40,0:06:30.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！等一下啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.15,0:06:33.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带漫画来是不被允许的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.99,0:06:35.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的，你这都第几次了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.16,0:06:38.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起，我们来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.08,0:06:41.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！阪津同学，身体没事了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.00,0:06:43.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.38,0:06:46.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么，快点回座位上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.90,0:07:09.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朝～仓～君～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.86,0:07:12.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊．．．嗯．．．这个不是我的．．．
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.28,0:07:18.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！喂喂，我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.71,0:07:28.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,松井君，休息的时间到我办公室来一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.89,0:07:39.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做了坏事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.93,0:07:41.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说谎是不对的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.93,0:07:45.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阪津同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.83,0:08:05.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久没来这里了，果然没什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.38,0:08:11.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是．．．是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.47,0:08:25.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那枝枪，是真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.60,0:08:29.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么，只是有点在意罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.56,0:08:32.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.11,0:08:34.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！学长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.24,0:08:39.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说今天早上有人看到你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.16,0:08:42.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就来找你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.54,0:08:50.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学长真是的，都被朝仓君听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.96,0:08:54.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！他不是客人啊！不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.17,0:09:36.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.30,0:09:40.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的，她一直都是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.18,0:09:44.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那．．我在这里多谢了，阪津
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.44,0:09:53.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赚到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.15,0:09:57.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来封住你的嘴巴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.49,0:10:03.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.87,0:10:06.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！久美
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.37,0:10:08.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在做什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.45,0:10:10.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也要一起来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.83,0:10:11.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优，走了啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.63,0:10:13.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.46,0:10:15.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.63,0:10:19.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.52,0:10:31.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住．．．住手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.94,0:10:39.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.79,0:10:53.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.33,0:10:56.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行，阪津同学，要出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.42,0:11:00.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是，叫我穗澄啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.38,0:11:01.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穗．．澄．．．
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.06,0:11:52.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是优君的哟，来舔一舔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.54,0:12:19.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛．．．痛．．．
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.01,0:12:33.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久美，你好狡猾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.21,0:13:06.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想射在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.25,0:13:40.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久美，你喜欢优君吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.08,0:13:42.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.42,0:13:43.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.06,0:15:21.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶，不快点的话就会融化掉了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.85,0:15:25.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烟火吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.53,0:15:35.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然出事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.91,0:15:39.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作孽，作孽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.87,0:15:47.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,南无阿弥陀佛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.18,0:15:59.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有没有后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.60,0:16:01.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.06,0:16:06.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你鹿这么想我很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.02,0:16:10.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我不是一个好女人，所以．．．
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.53,0:16:21.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我自己选择的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.16,0:16:27.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论大家怎么看\N我们三个人要永远在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.00,0:16:34.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不会再做那种事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.30,0:16:36.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后只和你做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.80,0:16:38.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真想早点有个孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.93,0:16:43.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要一直在一起哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.06,0:16:52.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起，我一个人睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.86,0:16:59.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们两人一直看着你的睡相哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.91,0:17:01.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久美很可爱哟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.05,0:17:14.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀啊啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.34,0:17:22.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,松井，你知道你在干什么吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.60,0:17:24.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道，少废话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.48,0:17:32.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！你．．．和我一起来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.98,0:17:35.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.82,0:17:37.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不走吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.95,0:17:39.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是．．是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.99,0:17:43.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！优
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.99,0:17:46.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,松井，你．．．
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.96,0:17:54.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在开始你们都是人质
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.43,0:18:08.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说是个普通的大学生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.19,0:18:11.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来是很普通的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.94,0:18:14.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然好像变了一个人似的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.69,0:18:18.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但愿不会太麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.53,0:19:00.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,森川警官，不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.90,0:19:01.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.16,0:19:03.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生了枪击案
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.74,0:19:06.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那枝枪吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.24,0:19:10.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道，只知道有一个人被刹了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.25,0:19:13.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犯人好像挟持了很多人质
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.50,0:19:18.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,报告人质的人数，并请特警队支援
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.01,0:19:21.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是，犯人只是一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.76,0:19:25.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我不愿这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.43,0:19:27.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过如果是那枝枪的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.10,0:19:29.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后应该还有受害者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.61,0:19:44.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.32,0:19:46.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本想在被抓之前享受一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.66,0:19:51.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是没用的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.08,0:19:57.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,松井，住手吧！去自首吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.88,0:19:59.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.30,0:20:03.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件事追根究底还是要怪你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.64,0:20:07.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想到一个好办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.89,0:20:09.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优，你把衣服脱了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.02,0:20:15.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.27,0:20:20.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么？不要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.03,0:20:25.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衣服脱了，很兴奋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.62,0:20:30.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菊地，中本！过来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.29,0:20:37.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这小子才是罪魁祸首
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.04,0:20:38.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他射到死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.88,0:20:40.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.84,0:20:44.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起，朝仓君
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.80,0:20:50.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.89,0:20:57.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恶心的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.64,0:22:13.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面情况怎么样？\N向我报告一下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.85,0:22:15.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突击队在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.14,0:22:16.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.48,0:23:08.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！岬，来吃我的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.57,0:23:10.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.82,0:23:15.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么．．．我就刹了他
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.59,0:23:28.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.13,0:24:15.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要！优，你起来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.14,0:24:19.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优～优～